==Competitive record==

===FIFA World Cup===
{{main|South Africa at the FIFA World Cup}}

Although [[South Africa]] has made three appearances in the [[FIFA World Cup|World Cup]], they have not made it past the first round. The team's first attempt to [[1994 FIFA World Cup qualification – CAF first round#Group D|qualify]] was for the [[1994 FIFA World Cup|1994 World Cup]], two years after they had been readmitted to FIFA. Their first appearance was in [[1998 FIFA World Cup|France 1998]]. Despite a 3–0 drubbing to [[France national football team|France]] in their opening game, they went on to draw against [[Denmark national football team|Denmark]] and [[Saudi Arabia national football team|Saudi Arabia]]; the team finished [[1998 FIFA World Cup Group C|third]] and thus exited the tournament. [[2002 FIFA World Cup|Korea/Japan 2002]] saw them eliminated in the [[2002 FIFA World Cup Group B|group stage]] again after drawing to [[Paraguay national football team|Paraguay]] and beating [[Slovenia national football team|Slovenia]] 1–0 for their first-ever World Cup win. The team finished third in their group, losing out to Paraguay on goal difference.

Hosting the [[2010 FIFA World Cup|2010 World Cup]], they famously upset [[France national football team|France]] 2–1 and drew 1–1 to [[Mexico national football team|Mexico]], but lost 0–3 to [[Uruguay national football team|Uruguay]]. They failed to advance to the round of 16, and became the first host country to fail to advance past the group stage. This would begin a long gap between appearances at the tournament for Bafana Bafana, but eventually ended after they qualified for the 2026 edition of the tournament.<ref>{{cite web |title=Performance of host countries in previous World Cups |url=https://www.tbsnews.net/sports/performance-host-countries-previous-world-cups-535430 |website=The Business Standard |date=20 November 2022 |access-date=November 20, 2022 |archive-date=20 November 2022 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20221120215053/https://www.tbsnews.net/sports/performance-host-countries-previous-world-cups-535430 |url-status=live }}</ref>

